@startuml RVBAlarm_StateMachine
title RVBAlarm State Machine

[*] --> IDLE

IDLE --> ON: MANUALSET\n[lamp blink, sirene blink]\nfor beeptime=2000ms
IDLE --> BASE_CALLING: SETSTARTED\n[lamp ON, sirene blink]

BASE_CALLING --> DONT_FLY: SETSTOPPED\n[lamp blink 0.5Hz, sirene blink 1s on/60s off]

DONT_FLY --> RESETTING: MANUALRESET | RESET\n[lamp blink, sirene blink]\nfor beeptime=2000ms
DONT_FLY --> BASE_CALLING: SETSTARTED\n[lamp ON, sirene blink]

ON --> DONT_FLY: timeout(flashtime)\n[lamp blink 0.5Hz, sirene blink 1s on/60s off]

RESETTING --> IDLE: timeout(flashtime)\n[lamp OFF, sirene OFF]

note right of IDLE
  Initial state
  All outputs OFF
end note

note right of BASE_CALLING
  Active alarm state
  Lamp: ON
  Sirene: blinking (500ms on/off)
end note

note right of ON
  Both lamp and sirene blinking
  Duration: beeptime (2000ms)
  Blink interval: beeponofftime (500ms)
end note

note right of DONT_FLY
  Alarm active (continuous)
  Lamp: blinking at 0.5 Hz (1s on, 1s off)
  Sirene: blinking 1000ms ON, 60000ms OFF
end note

note right of RESETTING
  Both lamp and sirene blinking
  Duration: beeptime (2000ms)
  Blink interval: beeponofftime (500ms)
end note

@enduml
